name: JShip
description:
Space exploration and spaceship builder game.

You can create and fly around with self-made spaceships. Mine resources with a laser and buy more parts and expand your spaceship more.The game is in a working state ,but i lost interest at one point and stopped working on it further.

I might touch it up a little and just release it as it is, but i dont know yet.

Oh and i almost forgot the coolest part: logic gates and wires -> you can connect pretty much all interactive parts with sensors and logic gates and in theory build a calculator in the game itself.
